<h3><a name="List"></a>List</h3>
<ul>
  <li><B>disappear()</B> - Makes the List not visible or touchable on the LCD.</li>
  <li><B>forceHit()</B> - List performs its &quot;hit&quot; method without user 
    input. The &quot;hit&quot; method will invoke all href functions of that object.</li>
    <li><B>forceUpdate()</B> - Forces the List to call its <B>initHref</B> function 
    immediately. Only valid if <B>initialCondition</B>&nbsp;is FromInitHref. 
    Updates the List and&nbsp;performs a &quot;hit&quot;.</li>
